Public: return index of row in NI Table FArray following a given time.

Parameters:
NIArray FArray with NI table returned by ObitTableNIUtilSwallow Rows each contain (all floats):
  • [0] Time - The center time (days)
  • [1] TimeI - Time interval of the solution
  • [2] antNo - Antenna number, 0=$>$ al
  • [3] SourId - Source number, 0=$>$ all
  • [4] SubA - Subarray number, 0=$>$ all
  • [5] weight - Weight
  • [6...] coef - Zernike model coeffients
time Target time in days, if time follows the last time in NIArray then returns index of the last row.
follow start search at index follow

row index in NIArray
